There is no way to update the users from CSV based on this documentation: [Importing Users from CSV Files|https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/CROWD/Importing+Users+from+CSV+Files]

{quote}If the Username already exists in Crowd, the CSV Importer does not overwrite the information for that user even if the Username exists in the CSV file with different user information.{quote}

I request the ability to update the existing users from CSV file.

I have seen this twice.

