2014-05-22 06:24:51,769 localhost-startStop-1 INFO [atlassian.plugin.manager.DefaultPluginManager] Plugin system started in 0:00:11.075
2014-05-22 06:24:51,789 localhost-startStop-1 INFO [ContainerBase.[Catalina].[localhost].[/crowd]] org.tuckey.web.filters.urlrewrite.UrlRewriteFilter INFO: loaded (conf ok)
